flowchart TD
    START([Start])
    A[Admin calls endElection]
    B[Contract phase = Ended]
    C[Contract internally determines winners]
    D[President: highest vote count]
    E[Secretary: highest vote count]
    F[Pass 1: top 2 female GMs by vote count]
    G[Pass 2: top 3 remaining GMs by vote count]
    H[Total: 7 winners determined]
    I[Admin calls startNewElection]
    J[Winner IDs written to electionResults]
    K[currentElectionId incremented by 1]
    L[Phase reset back to Created]
    START --> A --> B --> C
    C --> D --> I
    C --> E --> I
    C --> F --> G --> H --> I
    I --> J --> K --> L --> END([End])
